<li>Kenna, Kathleen; Stawicki, Andrew. (1995). <i>A People Apart</i>. New York: Houghton Mifflin Company. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0395673445" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-395-67344-5</a>.</li>
